    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she had to sell our house to Lithuanians for almost nothing just to make fare and to pay somebody, you know, there were people, you know, who did, you know, like black market, transferring people.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She gave them away all the money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he transferred, took [INAUDIBLE], made her a passport, a Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he smuggled her out from Lithuania to Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when she was in Poland, was already the Jewish organizations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there, she says, do you have relatives?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She says, I find out I have my two brother near Munich in a small little place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's called [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Dorfen ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Markt. ?] And she came there and we met all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my older sister was in Italy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Poland, she went to Italy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't see her till she came from Italy to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Israel she came to Canada.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we met in Canada.",
